Package bsiopis.webapp.entity

Class User

java.lang.Object
bsiopis.webapp.entity.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
User Entity Class. The base Entity class of the application, it consists of all the fields that store the data of the user. Connects with the database columns via Hibernate annotations. Also includes One-to-One mapping with the Address Entity.
Since:
2022-12-15
Version:
1.0
Author:
Bill Siopis
